1
00:00:30,880 --> 00:00:33,220
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:36,310
[Episode 15
Seeing Without a Heart]

3
00:00:37,880 --> 00:00:40,700
[Dedication Above Self]

4
00:00:45,170 --> 00:00:47,030
The sun is already high in the sky.

5
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:49,430
Lord Bai is usually here by now.

6
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:51,080
Why hasn't he shown up today?

7
00:00:53,830 --> 00:00:54,830
Something's off.

8
00:00:56,430 --> 00:00:57,240
Last night,

9
00:00:57,460 --> 00:00:59,360
His Lordship specially went through
all those backlogged scrolls

10
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:00,450
and reviewed them,

11
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:03,460
saying Xiqianhua would take over today.

12
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,120
Our county yamen

13
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:06,860
finally became independent from Xiqianhua.

14
00:01:06,860 --> 00:01:08,260
Why would it suddenly...

15
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,600
Effective immediately,

16
00:01:11,710 --> 00:01:15,289
Xiqianhua will temporarily take over
all affairs of the county yamen.

17
00:01:15,289 --> 00:01:18,910
Routine civil matters will be handled
by Deputy Magistrate Shi according to law.

18
00:01:18,910 --> 00:01:22,840
Complex cases and those involving demons
to be referred to Xiqianhua.

19
00:01:24,450 --> 00:01:25,260
Liu Fengling,

20
00:01:25,850 --> 00:01:26,970
what do you mean?

21
00:01:27,160 --> 00:01:27,870
Where is Lord Bai?

22
00:01:27,870 --> 00:01:29,200
Mind your own business.

23
00:01:29,990 --> 00:01:30,990
Miss Fanny.

24
00:01:31,460 --> 00:01:32,720
Lord Bai has already given instructions.

25
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:34,800
All the case files are right here.

26
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:41,020
Oh, right.

27
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,770
His Lordship told me

28
00:01:45,100 --> 00:01:46,160
to pass this letter

29
00:01:46,900 --> 00:01:48,259
to Lady Fufeng as well.

30
00:01:53,370 --> 00:01:54,039
My Lady.

31
00:02:00,860 --> 00:02:01,990
Do you think Lord Bai

32
00:02:02,710 --> 00:02:04,790
has resigned and returned to the capital?

33
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:06,520
But he was doing such a good job.

34
00:02:07,350 --> 00:02:08,680
He subdued the Wish Fox.

35
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:11,400
The people are all cheering for him.

36
00:02:13,940 --> 00:02:15,470
How should I know?

37
00:02:17,790 --> 00:02:18,790
Let's get to work.

38
00:02:26,540 --> 00:02:27,050
My Lady.

39
00:02:35,790 --> 00:02:36,350
Master,

40
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:38,790
County yamen's affairs have been arranged.

41
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:42,220
Deputy Magistrate Shi and Chen Xiaohu
will manage them for now.

42
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:43,030
In addition,

43
00:02:44,350 --> 00:02:46,350
Chen Xiaohu gave this to me.

44
00:02:47,260 --> 00:02:49,590
He said Lord Bai specifically instructed

45
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:51,730
that it must be given to you.

46
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:37,350
Lady Fufeng.

47
00:03:38,070 --> 00:03:39,730
May this letter find you well.

48
00:03:40,310 --> 00:03:43,040
Though my tenure
at Yin-Yang Crossing was brief,

49
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:46,150
the things I witnessed there
remain heavy on my heart.

50
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,820
There are unresolved matters

51
00:03:47,820 --> 00:03:48,910
I must speak of.

52
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:50,930
I hope you will hear me out.

53
00:03:52,650 --> 00:03:57,010
First, regarding education.
People like Wang Renjie at Qiuzhi Academy

54
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:59,940
have bullied the weak for a long time.

55
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:02,190
The root cause lies in the academy,

56
00:04:02,190 --> 00:04:05,590
imparting knowledge
while neglecting character building.

57
00:04:05,870 --> 00:04:09,870
I implore Your Ladyship to establish
new rules in the name of Xiqianhua.

58
00:04:10,350 --> 00:04:11,610
The academy's masters

59
00:04:11,620 --> 00:04:13,440
must pass a character assessment,

60
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:15,380
not be judged by scholarship alone.

61
00:04:15,380 --> 00:04:17,060
Breaking the barriers within their hearts

62
00:04:17,060 --> 00:04:18,790
is the only way to ensure lasting peace.

63
00:04:18,790 --> 00:04:21,269
Raising my wine cup to the blue sky.

64
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:26,360
Second, regarding the law.

65
00:04:27,590 --> 00:04:29,510
The disaster of the Wish Fox this time,

66
00:04:29,510 --> 00:04:30,540
at its root,

67
00:04:30,540 --> 00:04:31,740
is also a tragedy.

68
00:04:32,909 --> 00:04:35,540
Humans and demons have lived together
in Yin-Yang Crossing for centuries,

69
00:04:35,540 --> 00:04:38,240
yet the laws still largely
adhere to outdated systems.

70
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:40,670
I hope Your Ladyship will
push for new decrees

71
00:04:40,670 --> 00:04:43,530
to improve the system
of upbringing and education,

72
00:04:43,710 --> 00:04:47,640
and to perfect the regulation
and protection of marginalized beings.

73
00:04:51,340 --> 00:04:53,600
Third, regarding people's livelihood.

74
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:56,130
With this recent lockdown,

75
00:04:56,130 --> 00:04:58,240
we have seen the shadows lurking
beneath the glamour

76
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,500
of Yin-Yang Crossing.

77
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:01,870
The number of street beggars

78
00:05:01,950 --> 00:05:03,210
and homeless refugees

79
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:05,280
far exceeds what I had anticipated.

80
00:05:06,030 --> 00:05:08,790
I hope Your Ladyship can find a way
to check the household registers

81
00:05:08,790 --> 00:05:09,990
and teach them skills

82
00:05:10,540 --> 00:05:13,130
to earn a living with their own hands.

83
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:15,450
Only then can they truly settle down.

84
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:23,660
Postscript:

85
00:05:24,950 --> 00:05:26,470
Aside from official business,

86
00:05:26,470 --> 00:05:28,680
I also have a private word for Fufeng.

87
00:05:30,140 --> 00:05:32,570
Though that half-heart was never mine
to keep,

88
00:05:32,570 --> 00:05:34,500
it has resided within me for years.

89
00:05:35,150 --> 00:05:37,320
Now that it returns to its rightful owner,

90
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:40,590
let it serve as if
I am still by your side.

91
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:49,540
Bai Shanjun's last words.

92
00:05:55,659 --> 00:05:56,659
Bai Shanjun.

93
00:05:57,590 --> 00:05:59,270
You truly are a good man.

94
00:06:00,900 --> 00:06:05,070
It seems you prepared yourself
for everything last night.

95
00:06:36,450 --> 00:06:37,909
You are a good magistrate,

96
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:40,060
a good man.

97
00:06:42,300 --> 00:06:43,350
But so what?

98
00:06:45,970 --> 00:06:47,290
You just have bad luck.

99
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:08,750
How could I...

100
00:08:49,060 --> 00:08:51,030
This face is the real you.

101
00:08:52,060 --> 00:08:53,580
The magistrate who left the capital,

102
00:08:53,580 --> 00:08:56,110
and came to Yin-Yang Crossing
to take office—

103
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:57,910
Bai Shanjun.

104
00:08:58,870 --> 00:08:59,750
No wonder

105
00:09:00,540 --> 00:09:01,740
it feels so familiar.

106
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:06,910
You were born in the third year
of Jingping,

107
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:08,300
on the day of the Spring Equinox,

108
00:09:08,300 --> 00:09:09,900
at the third quarter of dusk.

109
00:09:10,870 --> 00:09:14,470
Spring Equinox, third watch,
the swallow bears the dawn's glow.

110
00:09:14,660 --> 00:09:17,540
Two moons aligned,
a green haze piercing the sky.

111
00:09:18,390 --> 00:09:20,250
Such an astronomical phenomenon

112
00:09:20,420 --> 00:09:21,870
is incredibly rare.

113
00:09:22,580 --> 00:09:24,300
The last time it appeared

114
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,390
was when I took out half of my heart.

115
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:31,030
So...

116
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:33,870
So Bai Han was bound to choose you

117
00:09:34,660 --> 00:09:36,030
as his vessel.

118
00:09:40,690 --> 00:09:43,050
You are the person in this world

119
00:09:43,700 --> 00:09:46,870
most compatible with my tree heart.

120
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:50,880
Only you can break the Treebound Curse
I planted.

121
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:52,670
And only you

122
00:09:53,930 --> 00:09:55,730
can bear my half-heart.

123
00:09:58,790 --> 00:09:59,700
Over the years,

124
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:01,380
he possessed many people.

125
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:03,990
But those people

126
00:10:04,110 --> 00:10:06,180
couldn't bear the power of my tree heart

127
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:07,300
and withered away,

128
00:10:07,630 --> 00:10:08,820
until he found you.

129
00:10:10,210 --> 00:10:12,810
Not only are you not consumed
by my tree heart,

130
00:10:13,300 --> 00:10:14,830
you actually merge with it.

131
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:19,270
That's why Bai Han

132
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:21,320
changed you into his appearance.

133
00:10:23,180 --> 00:10:25,850
What does it matter whose face it is?

134
00:10:27,210 --> 00:10:29,050
But I still want to thank you, My Lady,

135
00:10:29,050 --> 00:10:30,380
for telling me all this.

136
00:10:35,820 --> 00:10:36,630
My Lady,

137
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:40,540
why am I still alive?

138
00:10:43,940 --> 00:10:45,800
The tree heart has left your body,

139
00:10:46,660 --> 00:10:48,590
but some spiritual power remains.

140
00:10:49,530 --> 00:10:51,660
When the spiritual power dissipates,

141
00:10:52,060 --> 00:10:53,120
you will naturally

142
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,660
fade away.

143
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:05,330
If that's the case,

144
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,960
I will head back
to the county yamen first.

145
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:10,560
I won't disturb you, My Lady.

146
00:11:31,870 --> 00:11:32,700
Fengling

147
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:36,150
has already taken over the affairs
of the county yamen.

148
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:37,550
For your remaining days,

149
00:11:37,860 --> 00:11:39,860
rest and recover here in Xiqianhua.

150
00:11:42,150 --> 00:11:43,340
In Xiqianhua,

151
00:11:43,990 --> 00:11:45,520
sitting idle day after day,

152
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:47,180
waiting for death?

153
00:11:48,810 --> 00:11:50,670
If I can survive just one more day,

154
00:11:50,990 --> 00:11:52,940
I want to keep doing my duty

155
00:11:53,340 --> 00:11:55,400
for the people of Yin-Yang Crossing.

156
00:11:58,340 --> 00:11:59,150
As you wish.

157
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:18,350
My Lady,

158
00:12:19,270 --> 00:12:21,270
your heart has been returned to you,

159
00:12:22,070 --> 00:12:23,740
even if I die one day,

160
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:26,670
I will be at peace.

161
00:15:15,580 --> 00:15:16,910
Deputy Magistrate Shi.

162
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:21,420
Since Lord Bai went to Xiqianhua,

163
00:15:21,420 --> 00:15:23,420
there's been no word from him at all.

164
00:15:23,990 --> 00:15:26,190
Is our county yamen going to close down?

165
00:15:26,870 --> 00:15:27,460
Maybe

166
00:15:28,390 --> 00:15:29,850
we should all just go home.

167
00:15:31,340 --> 00:15:32,630
This is our home.

168
00:15:33,420 --> 00:15:35,910
His Lordship asked us to guard
the county yamen well,

169
00:15:35,910 --> 00:15:37,390
so we just follow orders.

170
00:15:37,870 --> 00:15:39,530
Of course you have to guard it.

171
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:42,630
Routine civil matters will be handled
by Deputy Magistrate Shi according to law.

172
00:15:42,630 --> 00:15:44,230
She didn't mention me at all.

173
00:15:44,630 --> 00:15:47,340
I'm telling you,
these officials from the capital,

174
00:15:47,340 --> 00:15:48,660
none of them treat this place as home.

175
00:15:48,660 --> 00:15:50,990
They only think about how to get promoted.

176
00:15:51,630 --> 00:15:53,420
Lord Bai is not that kind of person.

177
00:15:53,420 --> 00:15:54,910
Even if he gets promoted,

178
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:56,820
we should be happy for him.

179
00:15:57,820 --> 00:15:59,060
I don't want to go back.

180
00:15:59,060 --> 00:16:00,820
I want to be a constable.

181
00:16:06,700 --> 00:16:07,990
Where would I even go?

182
00:16:10,110 --> 00:16:10,660
My Lord.

183
00:16:10,740 --> 00:16:11,410
My Lord.

184
00:16:11,990 --> 00:16:13,720
I knew you hadn't forgotten us!

185
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:15,400
My Lord,

186
00:16:15,980 --> 00:16:18,770
you look terrible.

187
00:16:19,540 --> 00:16:20,790
It's nothing. Just a cold.

188
00:16:20,790 --> 00:16:21,750
I'll go find a doctor immediately.

189
00:16:21,750 --> 00:16:22,510
No need.

190
00:16:24,750 --> 00:16:28,150
Did anything happen
at the county yamen today?

191
00:16:29,990 --> 00:16:31,050
Nothing, nothing.

192
00:16:31,660 --> 00:16:34,420
Just the two vegetable gardens
on the East Street had a quarrel.

193
00:16:34,420 --> 00:16:36,460
I've already settled it.

194
00:16:43,110 --> 00:16:43,700
My Lord.

195
00:16:44,380 --> 00:16:45,710
You're clearly unwell,

196
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:47,820
and still looking through old cases?

197
00:16:47,820 --> 00:16:49,550
Please go rest in the back hall.

198
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:50,290
Yeah.

199
00:16:51,530 --> 00:16:52,330
It's nothing.

200
00:17:00,800 --> 00:17:03,930
The wine merchant was killed
on the north mountain road.

201
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:06,579
That was the first location
where the talisman appeared.

202
00:17:06,579 --> 00:17:09,300
And in the southwest, Qiutou Road,

203
00:17:09,619 --> 00:17:10,950
Zhou Ming was killed.

204
00:17:28,670 --> 00:17:29,580
Before he died,

205
00:17:29,950 --> 00:17:32,510
there was a talisman next to him.

206
00:17:34,190 --> 00:17:35,750
But there's no pattern.

207
00:17:37,340 --> 00:17:38,790
Where is it hidden?

208
00:18:15,900 --> 00:18:17,530
My Lady, don't worry about me.

209
00:18:17,530 --> 00:18:19,530
I can still hold on.

210
00:18:26,950 --> 00:18:27,510
My Lady,

211
00:18:31,100 --> 00:18:32,940
propriety demands distance
between a man and a woman.

212
00:18:32,940 --> 00:18:35,050
Please behave yourself, My Lady.

213
00:18:44,190 --> 00:18:45,030
Drink it.

214
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:47,060
If you collapse now,

215
00:18:47,750 --> 00:18:49,950
how can you work for Yin-Yang Crossing?

216
00:19:06,140 --> 00:19:08,710
Aren't you going to ask why I'm here?

217
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:11,860
Didn't you come to deliver medicine?

218
00:19:12,030 --> 00:19:12,900
Or could it be

219
00:19:13,900 --> 00:19:15,830
that you came out of concern for me?

220
00:19:17,710 --> 00:19:19,710
I'm here to return something to you.

221
00:19:20,820 --> 00:19:22,060
Since I gave it to you,

222
00:19:23,470 --> 00:19:24,620
it's yours.

223
00:19:31,430 --> 00:19:32,270
My Lady.

224
00:19:34,710 --> 00:19:35,910
My days are numbered.

225
00:19:36,730 --> 00:19:37,610
No...

226
00:19:37,860 --> 00:19:39,100
But I have no regrets.

227
00:19:43,230 --> 00:19:46,100
That half-heart has been returned to you,

228
00:19:46,950 --> 00:19:49,380
and Yin-Yang Crossing is now at peace.

229
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:52,300
Even if I die...

230
00:19:52,300 --> 00:19:53,560
Who allowed you to die?

231
00:20:08,670 --> 00:20:09,860
Rest well.

232
00:20:11,340 --> 00:20:12,140
We still

233
00:20:13,820 --> 00:20:14,790
need you here.
